# 386DX-40 harness — excluded from repo
# ROM and disk images are fetched/created locally (see docs/386/BRING-UP.md)

# HDD disk image (FreeDOS + DOOM)
*.img
*.hdf
*.vhd

# BIOS ROMs (fetched by fetch-roms.sh to ~/toolchains/emu/86box-roms)
roms/

# 86Box VM runtime dirs (created by run-386box.sh in /tmp)
